  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Using new tech to free 2 innocent Colombians</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Back in 2007 and 2009 (respectively), 2 Colombian citizens were accused of kidnapping and organized crime based on false testimonies; later condemned to heavy jail sentences (respectively 47 and 60 years). Gathering new evidence using of forensic technologies is their only hope to prove their innocence. Forensic tech. is indeed an expensive tool (around 7.500 USD for one complete investigation). But it has already had the greatest results in North America.</narrative>
  </description>
